{"type":null,"faqId":45457,"title":"可以用华为其他产品的遥控器控制华为盒子吗？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>秘盒采用的是蓝牙遥控器，按蓝牙遥控器 OK 键和音量+ </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165072\" style=\"width:0.29166666in;height:0.275in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，与华为盒子配对后，可以控制华为盒子。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>荣耀立方采用的是红外遥控器，与华为盒子键值基本相同（盒子比荣耀立方的遥控器少1个按键），可以通用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>荣耀盒子、华为盒子的红外遥控器与华为盒子键值完全相同，可以通用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"977","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557783000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":48,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"遥控,其他产品,控制","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}